    "en": {
      "title": "It is still raining at night",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, scattered rain or thundershowers will occur in the Central, Uva, Eastern, Northern and North Central provinces today (17) in the evening or during the night.",
        "A spokesman for the department said that there will be some rain in Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces, Galle and Matara districts.",
        "Thunderstorms may be accompanied by lightning and temporary gusty winds, the spokesman said."
      ],
